        <WHAT>_<WHERE>_<DESCRIPTION>
        <WHAT>: fg (foreground), bg (background), ic (icon), textColor (text color), special theme color names
        <WHERE>: widget name - button, switch, textInputLayout, etc.
        <DESCRIPTION>: context name (categories), detail name (image), state name (disabled)

        Naming examples:
        • fg_categories_image: <WHAT> - fg (foreground), <WHERE> - (not specified), <DESCRIPTION> - categories context, image detail
        • colorPrimary_button_profile_menu: <WHAT> - colorPrimary, <WHERE> - button, <DESCRIPTION> - profile context, menu detail
    -->

